title: Reebok Zig Kinetica 2.5 Chalk Alabaster
description: Reebok Zig Kinetica 2.5 'Chalk Alabaster' is a new edition of shoes that have a revolutionary cushioning system from 2010. ZigTech catches the eye with its wavy midsole while providing comfort and convenience. An additional overlay that you can put on further strengthens the trail style, perfectly matching the current trends.

title: adidas ADI2000 Sneakskin Stone Purple
description: adidas ADI2000 'Sneakskin Stone Purple' is a new proposition of the German brand, thanks to which you can forget about blending in with the gray crowd. The graphic on the upper imitates snakeskin, and translucent details refer to shoes from the early 2000s. Strong purple accents will emphasize your personality.

title: adidas Hyperturf Almost Yellow
description: Adidas Hyperturf 'Almost Yellow' are durable shoes that were inspired by the outdoor style. The modern upper combines suede, nubuck and a durable and tear-resistant ribstop fabric. Underfoot, you'll find soft Adiprene + cushioning foam for softness and comfort.

title: adidas by PHILLLLLTHY NMD_S1 Ambient Sky
description: adidas by PHILLLLLTHY NMD_S1 'Ambient Sky' is a new version of the iconic NMD model. This time the project was created in collaboration with the New York artist Philllip Leysa, widely known under the pseudonym Philllllty. Na Brooklyn is known for his unique patchwork vision, the use of previously used materials and the techniques of aging the items we wear. The upper consists of a mix of braided materials in beige and black, intertwined with blue inserts. The whole set on a sole with Boost material responsible for cushioning and comfort.

title: adidas Terrex Swift Solo 2
description: adidas Terrex Swift Solo 2 are men's trekking shoes, partly made of recycled materials. They will be perfect as shoes for mountain paths or a hard winter in the city. The grippy Traxion outsole and the Pro-Moderator system guarantee stability and very good traction. The upper of these shoes is made of durable, abrasion-resistant rip-stop fabric and synthetic overlays.

title: adidas Handball Spezial Collegiate Green
description: Adidas Handball Spezial are shoes that debuted in 1979 as a model for the world's best handball players, and today they are very popular thanks to their classic design and slim silhouette, also for casual football fans. The presented version was made of high-quality nubuck in a beautiful green color and was placed on a soft rubber outer sole. Iconic adidas three stripes in red complete the design.

title: Nike Air Force 1 Chili
description: It's time to turn up the heat with the Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Chili'. The edition was created for the 40th anniversary of one of the most famous models of all time. It is a tribute to tradition, culture and family. The upper consists of high-quality beige leather, complemented by hairy panels in a red color reminiscent of hot pepper. The title 'Chili' can still be seen on the heel and insole.

title: Nike Air Force 1 Mid WB Flax
description: Nike Air Force 1 Mid '07 WB 'Flax' is one of the most frequently chosen shoes of the American brand for the autumn-winter season. The high upper of this edition consists of high-quality nubuck in a golden-beige color, and the strap with a hook-and-loop closure protects the ankle not only from injury, but also from the cold. Stylish accessories such as a leather swoosh or round laces complete the whole. A full-length Nike Air unit is responsible for excellent shock absorption.

title: Nike Air Zoom Flight 95 White True Red
description: The Nike Air Zoom Flight 95 'White True Red' attracts attention with its futuristic design. Natural lines and distinctive details that mimic the eyes of an insect perfectly reflect the time when this silhouette was created. Originally designed for performance on basketball courts, the Zoom Air unit provides long-lasting cushioning and comfort, while the long tongue, curved midsole and embroidered details recall NBA dance floors from three decades ago.

title: Nike Air Max 270 White Game Royal
description: The Nike Air Max 270 'White Game Royal' is a dynamic silhouette combined with a visible Max Air 270 gas cushion that provides incredible comfort and style. The upper of these shoes is made of light knit and synthetic materials, together with the inner sock guarantee a perfect fit to the foot.

title: Reebok Smiley Instapump Fury Chalk
description: Iconic running shoes from the nineties, Reebok Smiley Instapump Fury 'Chalk' delight with new colors. They were created to celebrate the 50th anniversary of the iconic Smiley logo. The upper is made of many colors and materials, creating a unique style that no one will pass by indifferently.

title: adidas Forum 84 Low AEC White Red

It is not only about the same details, patterns and materials as the original edition, but also deliberately applied traces imitating their use. The shoes are made of a high-quality leather upper with nylon and synthetic leather accents. Some of the materials used for production come from recycling, among others production waste.

title: adidas by Sean Wotherspoon Hot Wheels Superturf Adventure
description: The presented adidas Superturf Adventure SW shoes were created thanks to the loud cooperation of adidas with Sean Wotherspoon and the Hot Wheels brand. The shoes are made of durable materials, and their silhouette is strongly inspired by trail silhouettes for mountain trips. The upper is made of durable leather and airy white mesh, complemented by colorful details. The zip fastener reveals the Hot Wheels dream slogan: 'It's not the same without the flame.' The culmination is Velcro on the heel to which we can attach various patches and a special box.

title: Reebok Pump Omni Zone II
description: The Reebok Pump Omni Zone II is an iconic basketball shoe that comes back in a classic color version. The white upper has been broken with standard Reebok accents in the form of blue and red. Thanks to Hexalite cushioning in the midsole, you get incredible comfort and cushioning, and the high collar above the ankle adds style. In the Reebok Pump Omni Zone II model he played, among others Dee Brown, 1991 dunk contest winner.
